#: ../../governance/index.md:57
msgid ""
"Traditionally, project leadership was unstructured but primarily driven by a"
" subset of Core Contributors whose active and consistent contributions have "
"been recognized by their receiving “commit rights” to the Project GitHub "
"repositories. In general all Project decisions are made through consensus "
"among the Core Contributors with input from the Community."
